SwissCheese.engine.texture

Class TexturePack

  • java.lang.Object
    • SwissCheese.engine.texture.TexturePack

  • public final class TexturePack
extends java.lang.Object
    A texture pack object that contains WallTextures to be used in game. A user can create their own texture packs which may eventually be added to the game natively. There will be an article on the SwissCheese wiki on creating a texturepack
    Since:
    2018-12-22, v0.5
    Version:
    v0.1
    Author:
    Alex Kalinins
